0.1.name: wordpress/jc-one-lite
0.1.description: Simple theme for clean, minimalistic and fast website. This theme uses the html5 boilerplate and is html5 ready. Make it yours with a custom background, menu. A configuration panel allow you to configure the color scheme (easy to include your own), the sidebars, the footer, social network, under construction page, fancybox support. JC One Lite has some basic shortcodes for making column layouts, beautyfull buttons, boxes, ...
